QuestData.Title: Supplies From the Skies
QuestData.Description: Are you feeling alright? Say 'ah.'$B$B<Mishka attempts to depress your tongue with a damp twig.>$B$BSorry... we are in desperate need of medical supplies here. The infirmary on the Skyfire was well-stocked, but it's all scattered to the winds now.$B$BAnything you can salvage from the wreck will save lives!
QuestData.RewardText: Just in time! I was about to start bandaging wounds with leaves.
